oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Wayne Castleman and Little Walter (undated)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: African Americans--Performances & portrayals; Castleman, Wayne;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color half sheet (black on white) announcing Wayne Castleman, Little Walter and the Mod Squad, Go Go Girls, and the Soulful Struts. Poster features metal photoplates of Wayne Castleman, Little Walter and the Mod Squad, Go Go Girls, and the Soulful Struts. Poster is undated and some of the metal photoplates have been crossed out with pen.
